    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3024927/" class="title-link">卖弄。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3024927"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/codezjl1103/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4602026-77.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/codezjl1103/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">轻舟</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-01"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-01 09:56:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3024927_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  正如他自己所言，文人最难戒是卖弄，包括他自己。这本书好思想固然不乏，但是卖弄说教的感觉太重。看得过程我很不爽。我是跳着看的，不觉得可惜。我已经被他影响太多，终于跳出崇拜他的圈子。哎，既然看得过程未为我带来舒心的感觉，给三星也不算辱没。

